content:
Prepare Your Agents to Use Bring Your Own Channel.

This article applies to: Bring Your Own Channel.

Create a custom permission set for your Bring Your Own Channel agents, and add the Message Customers with Bring Your Own Channel user permission.
Give your SCRT2 Integration User Read and Create access to the custom platform event for your Bring Your Own Channel messaging channel.
From Setup, in the Quick Find box, enter Permission Sets, and then select Permission Sets.
Click SCRT2 Integration User.
Click Object Settings.
Click the name of the custom platform event you just created.
Click Edit, and select the Read and Create checkboxes.
Click Save.
Create presence statuses for messaging.
Give your agents access to presence statuses.
title: Preparing Agents for Bring Your Own Channel in Service Cloud
